&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>量化资产管理</title><link>https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/index.html</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/index.html</guid><description>&lt;section class="book-cover"&gt;
 &lt;h1 class="book-cover-title"&gt;量化资产管理&lt;/h1&gt;
 &lt;p class="book-cover-subtitle"&gt;Quantitative Asset Management: Factor Investing and Machine Learning for Institutional Investing&lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;p class="book-cover-author"&gt;Michael Robbins&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;section class="book-intro"&gt;
 &lt;h2&gt;简介&lt;/h2&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;一本系统介绍因子投资与机器学习在机构资产管理中应用的实践指南。Robbins 以清晰的框架串联起从因子构建、组合优化到业绩归因的量化投资全流程，并深入探讨机器学习方法在资产定价和风险管理中的实际落地。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;h2 id="目录"&gt;目录&lt;a class="anchor" href="#%e7%9b%ae%e5%bd%95"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;








&lt;div class="book-toc-list"&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/partI.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第一部分 · 规划我们的工作&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;投资方程式——从产品定位到治理架构。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch01.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第01章 · 选择我们的产品&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;投资中的技术能力并非放之四海而皆准，本章讨论不同类型机构的目标、资源、约束与激励如何塑造投资管理的方式。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch02.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第02章 · 投资流程&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;既然我们已在第1章确定了自身在业务中的使命，并阐明了如何推进其目标&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch03.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第03章 · 领导力与治理&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;三种致命的投资错误——傲慢、无知与道德的随意——以及如何通过文化、商业论证、投资政策声明（IPS）和尽职调查来构建审慎治理与有效领导。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/partII.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第二部分 · 数据、特征与响应&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;资产类型、金融数据、特征工程与因子。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch04.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第04章 · 资产类型&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;本章将考察可用于决策的各类数据，并系统梳理股票、固定收益、大宗商品、另类投资等各类可投资资产的特征与差异。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch05.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第05章 · 金融数据&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;传统的统计和时间序列分析方法在处理金融数据的细微之处时往往力不从心&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch06.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第06章 · 特征&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;尽管人们普遍认为建模阶段占据预测过程的主要份额，但恰当选择特征往往对最终结果更为关键。本章讨论数据探索、抽样、可视化、特征的选择、处理与整理，以及缺失数据填补、异常值处理和合成数据生成等技术。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch07.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第07章 · 金融因子与经济因子&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;本章系统梳理量化投资中金融因子（financial factor）与经济因子（economic factor）的类别、构建与层级化建模方法，探讨风格因子、跨资产特征、另类数据及因子择时等关键议题。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch08.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第08章 · 构建因子预测&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;构建因子预测——从单因子到多因子模型，探讨因子组合、条件预测与机器学习方法。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch09.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第09章 · 策略、目标与条件&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;策略、目标与条件——如何将投资观点转化为可执行的目标函数与约束条件。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch10.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第10章 · 金融市场的时间序列与横截面分析&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;金融市场的时间序列与横截面分析——两种分析维度的方法、应用与组合。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/partIII.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第三部分 · 构建我们的流程&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;Alpha 与风险模型、资产配置、选股、回测、交易成本。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch11.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第11章 · Alpha 与风险模型&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;Alpha 与风险模型——收益预测模型与风险模型的协同设计，从单因子到集成模型。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch12.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第12章 · 资产配置&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;资产配置——战略配置、战术配置与选股的全流程，投资组合工厂的构建。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch13.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第13章 · 选股&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;选股——从宏观主题到量化打分，多策略组合内的证券选择方法。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch14.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第14章 · 回测&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;回测（backtesting）是验证系统化投资流程、建立信任并暴露模型缺陷的关键步骤。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch15.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第15章 · 交易成本与费用&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;交易成本与费用——显性费用与隐性市场冲击的建模、度量与优化。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch16.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第16章 · 再平衡与税收&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;再平衡与税收——投资方程式、税损收割与再平衡规则的成本效益分析。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch17.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第17章 · 金融市场的时间序列与横截面分析&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;我们在第二部分的结尾讨论了与该部分相关的算法。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/partIV.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第四部分 · 执行我们的计划&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;再平衡与税务、绩效与风险度量、投资与现金流管理。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch18.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第18章 · 绩效与风险度量&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;绩效与风险度量——自建还是外购、归因分析、风险分解与监控体系。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
 &lt;a class="toc-row" href="https://yuanuite.github.io/digital-library/books/quant-asset-management/ch19.html"&gt;
 &lt;span class="toc-row-title"&gt;第19章 · 投资、风险与现金管理&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-desc"&gt;战略计划是脆弱的，但这并不削弱规划的价值。本章系统梳理投资、风险与现金管理的治理、流程、文化与持续改进。&lt;/span&gt;
 
 &lt;span class="toc-row-arrow"&gt;›&lt;/span&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
